sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway API Gateway<br/>(Envoy Proxy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ExtProc as Payload Processing<br/>(BBR ExtProc Host)<br/>9004/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant ModelRes as model-provider-resolver<br/>plugin
    participant APITrans as api-translation<br/>plugin
    participant APIKey as apikey-injection<br/>plugin
    participant NemoReq as nemo-request-guard<br/>plugin
    participant NemoResp as nemo-response-guard<br/>plugin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant NemoSvc as NeMo Guardrails<br/>HTTP plaintext
    participant LLM as External LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: External Model Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Client token
    Gateway->>ExtProc: gRPC ExtProc request body<br/>9004/TCP, plaintext

    Note over ExtProc,APIKey: Plugin Pipeline (via CycleState)

    ExtProc->>ModelRes: Process request
    ModelRes->>ModelRes: Lookup model in<br/>in-memory modelInfoStore
    ModelRes-->>ExtProc: CycleState: provider info,<br/>credential refs

    ExtProc->>APITrans: Process request
    APITrans->>APITrans: Read CycleState provider info<br/>Translate OpenAI → provider format<br/>(Anthropic/Azure/Bedrock/Vertex)
    APITrans-->>ExtProc: Mutated request body +<br/>:path header rewrite

    ExtProc->>APIKey: Process request
    APIKey->>APIKey: Read CycleState credential refs<br/>Lookup in-memory secretStore<br/>Inject auth header
    APIKey-->>ExtProc: Authorization header added

    opt NeMo Guardrails Enabled
        ExtProc->>NemoReq: Process request
        NemoReq->>NemoSvc: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP plaintext, No auth
        NemoSvc-->>NemoReq: Allow / Block decision
        alt Request Blocked
            NemoReq-->>ExtProc: 403 Forbidden
            ExtProc-->>Gateway: gRPC response: 403
            Gateway-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
        end
        NemoReq-->>ExtProc: Request allowed
    end

    ExtProc-->>Gateway: gRPC response:<br/>mutated headers + body
    Gateway->>LLM: Translated request<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Provider-specific API key
    LLM-->>Gateway: Provider response
    Gateway->>ExtProc: gRPC ExtProc response body

    ExtProc->>APITrans: Process response
    APITrans->>APITrans: Translate provider → OpenAI format<br/>Strip provider-specific fields
    APITrans-->>ExtProc: Normalized response body

    opt NeMo Guardrails Enabled
        ExtProc->>NemoResp: Process response
        NemoResp->>NemoSvc: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP plaintext, No auth
        NemoSvc-->>NemoResp: Allow / Block decision
        alt Response Blocked
            NemoResp-->>ExtProc: Blocked response
            ExtProc-->>Gateway: gRPC response: blocked
            Gateway-->>Client: Policy violation response
        end
        NemoResp-->>ExtProc: Response allowed
    end

    ExtProc-->>Gateway: gRPC response:<br/>mutated response body
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+

    Note over K8sAPI,ExtProc: Flow 2: ExternalModel/Secret Reconciliation (background)

    K8sAPI-->>ModelRes: Watch events: ExternalModel CRs<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, SA Bearer token
    ModelRes->>ModelRes: Update in-memory modelInfoStore<br/>(RWMutex synchronized)

    K8sAPI-->>APIKey: Watch events: labeled Secrets<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, SA Bearer token
    APIKey->>APIKey: Update in-memory secretStore<br/>(RWMutex synchronized)
